title: Level 5 Champs

I only play champions I have mastery rank 5 in ranked (for the bm emote spam when I die)

I only play champions I don't have rank 5 on in norms (and I stick to 3 champs per role till they reach max mastery).

I love the mastery system, the only downside is that people assume you are going to be perfect at a champion once you hit rank 5. People can still have bad games, and on top of this you can reach rank 5 by losing your way there (my tristana games tbh).
